How to make a bread-pizza
Ingredients: 
1. bread
2. pizza sauce
3. cheese
4. any other topping (optional)

Steps- 
1. Take a loaf of bread
2. Spread a layer of pizza sauce on it.
3. Spread a layer of cheese.
4. Add any other topping you want (optional)
5. You can heat the pizza in a pan for 2-3 minutes.
~Your bread-pizza is ready~